## üîå API Endpoints

### Threat Detection (8 endpoints)

```bash
POST /api/shield/threats/analyze          # Analyze request for threats
POST /api/shield/threats/login-attempt    # Analyze login attempt
POST /api/shield/threats/network-traffic  # Analyze network traffic
GET  /api/shield/threats                  # List threats
GET  /api/shield/threats/{id}             # Get threat details
GET  /api/shield/threats/blocked-ips      # Get blocked IPs
POST /api/shield/threats/block-ip         # Block IP
POST /api/shield/threats/unblock-ip       # Unblock IP
```

### AI Anomaly Detection (3 endpoints)

```bash
POST /api/shield/anomaly/user-behavior    # Analyze user behavior
POST /api/shield/anomaly/api-usage        # Analyze API usage
POST /api/shield/anomaly/zero-day         # Detect zero-day threats
```

### Incident Response (3 endpoints)

```bash
GET  /api/shield/incidents                # List incidents
GET  /api/shield/incidents/{id}           # Get incident details
POST /api/shield/incidents/{id}/respond   # Respond to incident
```

### Vulnerability Scanning (3 endpoints)

```bash
POST /api/shield/vulnerabilities/scan     # Scan for vulnerabilities
GET  /api/shield/vulnerabilities          # List vulnerabilities
GET  /api/shield/vulnerabilities/report   # Get vulnerability report
