## üöÄ Deployment

### Standalone Deployment

```yaml
# docker-compose.yml
services:
  itechsmart-shield:
    image: itechsmart/shield:latest
    ports:
      - "8007:8000"
    environment:
      - STANDALONE_MODE=true
      - DATABASE_URL=postgresql://user:pass@db:5432/shield
```

### Integrated Deployment

```yaml
# docker-compose.yml
services:
  itechsmart-shield:
    image: itechsmart/shield:latest
    ports:
      - "8007:8000"
    environment:
      - HUB_URL=http://enterprise-hub:8000
      - STANDALONE_MODE=false
      - DATABASE_URL=postgresql://user:pass@db:5432/shield
```

